# AI Usage LINKS

## Overview

Artificial Intelligence tools (ChatGPT) were used throughout the development of this project to support coding, debugging, and design decisions.

The use of AI was aligned with the coursework requirements and all outputs were manually reviewed and validated.

---

## How AI Was Used

AI assistance was used for the following tasks:

- Generating the initial structure of the Streamlit application
- Writing and refining data cleaning functions (missing values, duplicates, outliers)
- Implementing transformation logic (scaling, encoding, feature creation)
- Designing the user interface (layout, styling, user flow)
- Debugging errors during development
- Supporting deployment on Streamlit Cloud
- Improving documentation (README and report structure)

---

## Verification Process

All AI-generated outputs were:

- Carefully reviewed and tested manually
- Modified where necessary to ensure correctness
- Validated through execution in the Streamlit application

No AI output was used without verification.

